Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}簡直就像在主張自己是怪物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 不時露出的這種眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}簡直像被觀察著一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}妳肯給我生孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}四郎 快點回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然後有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}媽媽 為什麼要欺負夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}於是我喜歡上了疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為疼痛讓我感到這是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}溫柔什麼的不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託你了 四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再打我一次吧
